name: dacite
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "dacite" %}
{% set version = "1.6.0" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: d48125ed0a0352d3de9f493bf980038088f45f3f9d7498f090b50a847daaa6df

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
    - dataclasses
  run:
    - python
    - dataclasses

test:
  imports:
    - dacite
  requires:
    - pip
  commands:
    - pip check

about:
  home: "https://github.com/konradhalas/dacite"
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "Simple creation of data classes from dictionaries."

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - mands
